    {
      "levelGroup": "intermediate",
      "title": "Navigating Like a Local",
      "cefrLevel": "B1",
      "summaryJa": "知らない場所で道を聞く際、より自然で丁寧な表現を使って目的地までたどり着く方法を学びます。",
      "sourceUrls": [
        "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/topics/evergreen/travel_culture/asking-for-directions"
      ],
      "sentences": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "text": "Excuse me, I am sorry to bother you, but I am looking for the museum.",
          "translationJa": "すみません、お忙しいところ恐縮ですが、博物館を探しています。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s01",
          "startMs": 0,
          "endMs": 4280,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s01.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "text": "I think I have taken the wrong turn somewhere near the main city square.",
          "translationJa": "メイン広場の近くで道を間違えてしまったようです。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s02",
          "startMs": 4680,
          "endMs": 8310,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s02.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 2,
          "text": "Could you point me in the right direction to reach the entrance safely?",
          "translationJa": "入り口まで行く正しい方向を教えていただけますか？",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s03",
          "startMs": 8710,
          "endMs": 11947,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s03.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 3,
          "text": "It is quite confusing to navigate around these narrow and winding local streets.",
          "translationJa": "これらの狭くて曲がりくねった通りを歩くのは少し混乱します。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s04",
          "startMs": 12347,
          "endMs": 16593,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s04.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 4,
          "text": "You need to walk past the large fountain and keep heading towards the library.",
          "translationJa": "大きな噴水を通り過ぎて、図書館に向かって歩き続けてください。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s05",
          "startMs": 16993,
          "endMs": 20770,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s05.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 5,
          "text": "Once you reach the traffic lights, you will see the museum on your left.",
          "translationJa": "信号機に着いたら、左手に博物館が見えるはずです。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s06",
          "startMs": 21170,
          "endMs": 25015,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s06.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 6,
          "text": "Is it within walking distance, or should I take a bus from this stop?",
          "translationJa": "徒歩で行けますか、それともこの停留所からバスに乗るべきですか？",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s07",
          "startMs": 25415,
          "endMs": 29116,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s07.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 7,
          "text": "It is only a ten-minute walk if you take the shortcut through the park.",
          "translationJa": "公園を通る近道を使えば、徒歩でわずか10分です。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s08",
          "startMs": 29516,
          "endMs": 32926,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s08.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 8,
          "text": "That sounds perfect, thank you so much for your clear and helpful instructions today.",
          "translationJa": "それは素晴らしいですね。今日はずっと分かりやすい説明をありがとうございます。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s09",
          "startMs": 33326,
          "endMs": 37980,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s09.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 9,
          "text": "You are very welcome, I hope you enjoy your visit to the museum today.",
          "translationJa": "どういたしまして。今日の博物館訪問を楽しんでくださいね。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s10",
          "startMs": 38380,
          "endMs": 42331,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s10.m4a"
        },
        {
          "index": 10,
          "text": "I appreciate your kindness and have a pleasant afternoon in the city, my friend.",
          "translationJa": "親切に感謝します。友よ、この街で良い午後を過ごしてください。",
          "id": "intermediate-2026-07-04-s11",
          "startMs": 42731,
          "endMs": 47058,
          "sentenceAudioUrl": "https://shoya9696.github.io/daily-shadowing-content/audio/2026-07-04/intermediate-s11.m4a"
        }
      ],
